Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can buy a real sword\Nfor that paltry amount of money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not gonna buy anything, scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry that we tried to extort you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry about it!\NThanks for showing me the way! Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the brats who showed me the way that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-san! Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be our big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mothers Are Strong!\NZoro's Hectic Household Chores!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I refuse.\N--What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to become a\Nbig brother to brats like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having seen you beat marines,\Nwe've taken quite a liking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Michael. Glad to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hoichael.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the backstreets,\Nwe brothers are a bit famous for...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should hear people out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, we'll take you wherever you wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go buy some meat?\NHow about vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I refuse.\N--You refuse? Refuse what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both becoming your big brother\Nand having you show me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, that's right!\NBro, you're looking to buy a sword, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sword shop owner turned me down earlier,\Nsince I don't have much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should go to a secondhand store.\NI bet you'll find quite a bargain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! We'll show our big brother\Nthe way to the secondhand store!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it couldn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me just point out that I'm not\Nagreeing to become your big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, make way, make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter Zoro-sama coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:05:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're skipping school\Nand wandering about again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna grow up to be\Ngood-for-nothings. What ungrateful kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at their home,\Nit's rather the mother that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for those kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So no luck here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rude to Big Bro Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that swordsman who's with them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one of the pirates who saved Iceberg-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? I thought he was a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's just a punk? I misjudged him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have got quite a reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The townspeople are clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can say whatever they\Nwant about us. We don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? Good for you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you abandoning your dear little brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I don't remember\Nbecoming your big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I shook them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Bro! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know this town like the back of our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can get away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop mocking me, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's harsh, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me "Bro"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what do you think\Nyou're doing, hitting my kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My kids"? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What strength! What's with this woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Not bad, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:08:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Special Attack! Bam-Bam Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Mom! He didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all our fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were misbehaving again?! You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it's okay, right,\Nsince you became their big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, come out and say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm Shou.\N--I'm Ayako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, this is Big Bro Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our new oldest brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oldest brother...? Don't tell me you\Nwant me to be your big brother for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us. We're behind\Nwith our household chores,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since we've had to spend a lot of time\Nrepairing our house after Aqua Laguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! I didn't agree to this!\NLet go of me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go home, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Mom is out working,\Nwe go pick up scrap wood at the harbor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while we're babysitting our siblings,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and once we get enough wood,\Nwe go sell it to Galley-La on the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can make quite a bit of\Nallowance money that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, say goodbye to your mom for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but this has nothing to do with me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Geez...\N--Nice babysitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, you're good with babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:10:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He wet himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go change his diaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What're you doing?!\NWhat are you, a perv?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna wash it. Wear this until it's dried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, kids! Let's work hard\Nand clean up the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hoichael. Sorry, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Michael! Do something about these...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where do I put these...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite a natural at this. Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, be good, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lady. I'm going back now.\NGive me my shirt back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have a place to\Ngo back to besides this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. My friends are waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid! Friends or family--\Nwhich one's more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your family. I don't\Nremember you giving birth to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're not blood-related, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! The hell with blood relationships!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are blood relationships that important?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna settle this today for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here yesterday and the day before,\Nbut you didn't pay us back, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've seen you somewhere before.\NAnother new family member?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right.\N--No.\N--Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's not like you're\NPaulie from Galley-La.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit dragging your feet\Nand pay us back, you old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you before, I already\Npaid back what I borrowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool. Debts come with interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That interest also accrued more interest,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's now several dozen times more\Nthan the amount you borrowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of my concern.\NWhy don't you pay it yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, you damn old hag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you to suffer all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you work those brats hard,\Nyou can earn money easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not your real family anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:13:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they don't look alike at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt! What're you doing, you old hag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say that one more time,\Nand I'll blow your head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'll let you off the hook for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cool!\N--Just as we'd expect from you, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy. Mom's proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--"Good boy"...?\N--Okay, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go shopping for dinner, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up. You're coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a job for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, knock the price down a bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're dealing with?!\NDon't take us lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! However you look at it,\Nthis doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do things like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they see me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all people, it had to be that damn cook...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that alley over there is a shortcut? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:15:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've come this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you're having a rough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, tell me about it.\NHow could this be happening to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dammit!\N--Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and... that look suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough! I'm going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're going home ahead of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll give you the key to the house.\NClean the restroom or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm not going back to your house!\NI'm going back to my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's speaking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak like that to your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you Broccoli Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Broccoli Head! It's Moss Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Moss Head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, Moss Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Hey, no! That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do with my oldest son?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael, Hoichael. Go get him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your bodyguard is gone,\Nso I'd like to continue our discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you come with me for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoichael, go get Bro.\NI bet they'll take us to that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your family. I don't\Nremember you giving birth to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're not blood-related, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! The hell with blood relationships!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are blood relationships that important?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, there's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The debt collector took our mom away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but it has nothing to do with me.\NAnd that lady can take care of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, he brought a bunch of his buddies
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and took Michael and my siblings away, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:18:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure got cocky with me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As thanks for that, I brought\Nsome scary guys with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared out of your wits!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! Please come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the captain of the\NBig Helmet Pirate Gang, Mikazuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a 36-million-Berry bounty on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids, stay back. Don't do anything, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikazuki-san has a vicious past.\NHe tried to walk out of Dock #1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at Galley-La without paying\Nfor the repair of his ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...although he was regrettably\Ndefeated by Galley-La's foremen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, in order to earn money for the repairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's been earnestly working\Npart-time at our company and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys, think hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about which is better--hurrying up\Nand paying so you can survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or defying me and becoming prey for my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you five seconds to think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You wanna fight with me,\Nthe great Mikazuki-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool. As mentioned already,\Nmy bounty is 36 million Berries, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang-Bang Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An attack like that won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where they took them to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They always take people to the\Nsame place. We've seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take a man with a\N36-million bounty lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you kids to stay back!\NDon't do anything dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying, Mom?! We're a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a family for if we\Ndon't help each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sassy thing to say, you stupid son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, teach them a lesson\Nthey won't soon forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You small fry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventy-two Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Incredible!\N--Just as we'd expect from you, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Good job! That's my oldest son!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still saying that? Hey, lady. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, to start with, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your friends as good as our family?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you tell me sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you a bunch of times!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a member of our precious family,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but, well, if you're gonna run away\Nfrom home for a bit, I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Run away from home"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, congrats on running away from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go now before\NMom changes her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take care!\N--Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you!\N--See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come this far. I should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never learns, does he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.78,0:22:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't run from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, he forgot to change his shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do with my oldest son?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I said, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, don't pull me, Chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma told me about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.81,0:22:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stall, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, pops! How're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A petty stall like this wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Looks like the cook here\Nis better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sanji's Shock! Mysterious Old Man\Nand His Super Yummy Cooking!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
